creator: Virtuagym Professional
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to HZO World of Sports!

This app is the virtual home of the adidas World of Sports - HZO GYM, Company Sports, and Outdoor Sports - on the adidas HQ campus in Herzogenaurach, Bavaria, Germany.

PLEASE NOTE: ONLY adidas HQ employees and selected associated have access to this app.

This comprehensive platform offers everything from memberships, to class schedules and information, opening hours, booking tools, communications and much more.

We look forward to welcoming YOU to the World of Sports - a holistic growth environment and unique experience. A place where fun meets movement.
